File: The DA's Eastern Cape leader, Nqaba Bhanga, is the new Mayor of Nelson Mandela Bay. (eNCA) JOHANNESBURG - Eastern Cape Cogta MEC, Xolile Nqatha has declared Nqaba Bhanga's election as Mayor of Nelson Mandela Bay invalid. The DA Eastern Cape leader was elected over the weekend following a long and dramatic meeting. READ: Nqaba Bhanga elected NMB Mayor This is a developing story.